msgid "Show the Demo submenu in the Patcherly admin menu"
msgstr "Mostra il sottomenu Demo nel menu di amministrazione di Patcherly"

#: connectors/patcherly/patcherly.php:1269
msgid "When ON (default), wp-admin shows a \"Demo (explore)\" submenu with a fully mocked Errors page so you can preview Patcherly before pairing. The demo never calls the Patcherly API, never makes AI calls, and never writes to your database. Untick to hide the submenu once you no longer need it."
msgstr "Quando è ATTIVO (impostazione predefinita), wp-admin mostra un sottomenu \"Demo (esplora)\" con una pagina Errori completamente simulata che ti permette di provare Patcherly prima dell'accoppiamento. La demo non chiama mai l'API Patcherly, non effettua mai chiamate IA e non scrive mai nel tuo database. Disattivalo per nascondere il sottomenu quando non ti serve più."

#: connectors/patcherly/patcherly.php:1276
msgid "Enable local debug log of Patcherly API calls"
msgstr "Abilita il log locale di debug per le chiamate all'API Patcherly"

#. %d is the maximum number of debug entries kept locally
#: connectors/patcherly/patcherly.php:1279
#, python-format
msgid "When ON, the plugin records a sanitized log of every call it makes to Patcherly (what was called, when, how long it took, whether it succeeded) and shows it in a new \"Debug\" submenu. Your credentials, signatures, and the contents of every request and response are NEVER captured. The log lives only on your site, is capped at %d entries, and is deleted from your database the moment you turn this OFF. No data ever leaves your site."
msgstr ""

#: connectors/patcherly/patcherly.php:1283
msgid "Open the Debug page →"
msgstr "Apri la pagina di Debug →"

#: connectors/patcherly/patcherly.php:1295
msgid "No database data, user data, or site content is ever shared, sent, or stored in Patcherly. We do not need that kind of data — we only use technical information about your site (such as software versions, database technical version (not the data in it), and, if you choose Full or Minimal, plugin and theme names). No sensitive data is ever sent off your site or memorized elsewhere."
msgstr ""

